  <brief_title>Double Filtration Plasmapheresis (DFPP) and Lipid Metabolism</brief_title>
  <official_title>Double Filtration Plasmapheresis (DFPP) Improves Lipid Profile and Platelet Function in Hyperlipidemia Patients</official_title>
